Zetsash indirectly represents the [[overlord]] [[Masvirik]], the Cold Sun, on the [[Bleak Council]] of [[Ashtakala]]. While the [[dragon]] [[Rhashaak]] is technically the [[speaker|prakhutu]] of Masvirik, he is bound to [[Haka'torvhak]], so the reptilian [[rakshasa]] Zetsash carries out Rhashaak's will amidst the plots of the [[Lords of Dust]].